premise_source_doc_sentence: Olivia Wilde  (  born Olivia Jane Cockburn ; March 10 , 1984  )  is an American actress , model , director , and producer .

She is well known for her role as Dr. Remy `` Thirteen '' Hadley on the award-winning medical television series House  (  2007 -- 12  )  and her roles in Alpha Dog  (  2007  )  , Tron : Legacy  (  2010  )  , Cowboys & Aliens  (  2011  )  , Her  (  2013  )  , Drinking Buddies  (  2013  )  , and Rush  (  2013  )  .
She starred in HBO 's rock 'n' roll drama series Vinyl  (  2016  )  .
